      "writtenOn": "2020-09-18T00:24:23Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "`CurrentItemOrder()` need to return an error because there may be errors when serializing a key or property.. \n\nCapturing the static itemOrder and using []*iteratorEntry instead of []*queryIterator is for time saving. Otherwise, it needs to dynamically serializing to item order each time for `heap.pop` and `heap.push`.",
